value.string: This custom home is a high end ocean front residence with the best views on the North Shore of Maui. As one enters they are engulfed with the deep blue ocean and the vistas from the lanai stretch from Paia Bay to Kahakuloa to the west and Hookipa to the east. The home has 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths and includes a detached caretaker’s home of 1 bedroom/1bath and 600 sq ft of living area. This beach style estate commands the view from the point of land on approximately 29,000. The home is built with quality materials with fine craftsmanship and privacy in mind. This is a one of a kind property and a rare opportunity to own a jewel in Paia with the security of a gated driveway in an upscale development. Come join us for a showing of this beautiful property today! Listor must be present for all showings. Tenant occupied. Please allow 24 hours for showings.

Spectacular gated oceanfront estate on almost one acre of beautifully landscaped grounds. Classic Plantation style residence with true Hawaiian ambience offering private ocean acces and sand for enjoying the Maui oceanfront lifestyle. A separate ohana can be utilized for guests or as a nanny / caretaker's quarters. This phenomenal shoreline setting provides the most amazing ocean views, neighboring island views of Lanai and Molokai, and year-round sunset views. Turtles abound with whale watching in season. Other features include a large tiled pool, fireplace, 3-car garage, and private well for irrigation. Offered furnished for immediate enjoyment.

This masterfully built oceanfront residence consisting of uncompromising craftsmanship welcomes you to the North Shore with a turn-key opportunity. Offered fully furnished, 27 Lae Place offers 4,282 square feet of open living space with 5 private bedroom retreats and 4.5 beautifully appointed bathrooms. Resting directly on the oceans edge, 27 Lae Place has incredible views of the West Maui Mountains sunset and even the neighboring island of Molokai. Within minutes of the world famous Paia Town 27 Lae Place lends convenience and privacy to the discerning buyer. A large oceanfront lap pool has been painstakingly approved and built that allows for sunset swims and fun for the family. This home is an ideal North Shore property for someone who enjoys oceanfront living, privacy and a "Paddle in Paddle out" lifestyle.

Very private & gated home is direct ocean front with just minimal steps to the water. This home is located on a small street with only 7 homes. Subject was totally rebuilt in 2009. This home has all new plumbing, electrical wiring both inside and outside, All new Kitchen and Bath with upstairs Master suite. Small sandy beach steps from this home where you can enjoy beautiful sunsets, whale watching , launch your Stand Up Paddle board, or enjoy a beverage while watching the boats coming in out of the Maalaea Harbor.

Experience peace and serenity from this expansive oceanfront home. Newly Furnished and staged to Sell, this Farrington Bayless designed home incorporates traditional kama’aina living on the spectacular North Shore of Maui. This home is primarily single level, with master suites and en-suite bedrooms with ocean views that open to the fresh air and sea breeze, all with warm finishes. The residence includes a total of 4 bedrooms, 4 ½ baths, den/media room, records/storage room, art gallery, a chef’s kitchen with oversized island, laundry/utility room, office nook, 3 car garage, gym, and separate 1 bedroom 1 bath Ohana/house with separate gated entry. Master suite includes steam room and sauna, walk out shower and walk in closet overlooking your own Japanese inspired rock garden. The grand two story living room with 25 ft. ceilings, colossal fireplace, art gallery aloft, and great room accommodate formal entertaining, while the over-sized eat-in kitchen flowing out to wide lanai with pool and spa with infinity edge sets the relaxing atmosphere for casual gatherings with family and close friends. Simply understated perfection!

Perched upon Maui's East shores, atop gentle sea cliffs sliding into a private cove, this Heavenly Hana estate is truly one of a kind. One can truly enjoy the cross-section of modern architecture and historic charm while escaping into total serenity, peace and quiet. Every inch of this 3.5 acre property has been strategically planned, with Asian gardens meandering between tropical Hawaiian landscaping, flowing out to expansive park like grass bluffs. The classic architecture of the 2 dwellings, encompassing almost 4,000 sq ft all together, have been totally rebuilt using heavy cement and tile construction providing durability for ocean front living. Enjoy beautiful deck and outdoor space, a green house, multi car garage, an in ground pool, entertaining pavilion, beautiful paved pathways, security gates, guest cottage, and a landscape that words simply can't describe. Truly Heavenly, Truly Harmonious, Truly Hana.

Beautiful OCEANFRONT ISLAND STYLE HOME on Kahana Bay; offering approx. 200 feet of direct ocean frontage and AMAZING VIEWS, can't get closer to the ocean! This large home's design is inspired with upscale Island living in mind! The "Bali House" offers four Master Suite bedrooms all with massive ocean views! There are two other optional bedrooms and a great Gourmet Kitchen! Beautiful private tropical grounds feature a saltwater pool, water fall and spa with VIEWS of the Lanai and Molokai as your backdrop for daily Sunsets! Property is being offered furnished and includes many other spaces and features not listed here! Shown by advance appointment only!

Just steps to the water's edge. And there are steps. What a lovely setting this property has. This property is located about 3 miles from town next to an ancient fishpond and has rock walls and fencing that surround the whole property. This nicely landscaped yard sits on a half acre of land with some fruit trees and an above ground swimming pool. At night you can sit on the deck and see the sunset most of the year over the water, and later see the stars shine bright at night. On Molokai, you can see endless stars. During the winter months you see the humpbacks breaching in the channel in front. It's a perfect place to launch your paddling toys and paddle over our pristine barrier reef. They have cleared the fishpond of mangrove so there is a very nice view of the fishpond looking towards Maui. The house has 2 bedrooms and 2 bath, nice size living area and remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances and enclosed sitting area and A/C in most rooms.

Handsomely perched over water’s edge w/ 160 ft. of direct ocean frontage stands this residence & detached cottage. Experience the finest materials & craftsmanship in a very special & private oceanfront setting. Vibrant hibiscus flowers & sounds of the ocean liven the senses as you approach the 14ft. ‘ohia poles-the gateway into what is unequivocally the top valued oceanfront residence on Maui. Many large windows afford prime vantage points to remain intimately connected from any point in the entire home to ocean, Haleakala, and Maalaea Harbor vistas abound. Your new home was completely remodeled (most recently as 2011) w/ a plethora of exotic hardwoods, surfaces, & finishes. Envision Venetian plaster, Travertine, & Hawaiian Koa-it all lives here & more, in a perfect state of balance & sophistication. The great room redefines the open concept for living, dining, food & timeless memory creation. A massive solid monkeypod kitchen island that is only rivaled by the one which this residence calls home is stylishly accented by mango cabinetry, exotic granite slabs, & superior stainless appliances. On the lanai, sliding glass walls disappear, soothing sounds of lightly crashing waves emerge, and the ten resident turtles smile up at you. 3 of the 4 bedrooms are suites each w/ their own distinctive elegance & all with perfectly framed views. Book your first class tickets, prepare your $4m wire transfer, & get your appointment today- this is a true steal & you will regret not owning this home.

Situated on an Exceptional one acre Oceanfront parcel, surrounded by palm trees and gentle breezes, this amazing island home is reminiscent of the classic Maui Beach House! Enjoy the peace and tranquility of Hana and this truly special property, as you meander down quiet Kapohue Road lined with Hawaiian rock walls and cascading trees. One will be immediately captivated by the unsurpassed ocean views beyond the rolling lawns, sounds of the surf, swaying palms and your own private lookout point! Surrounded by large covered decks with endless views of the ocean and mountains of Hana, this island home features three bedrooms, 4 full baths, a spacious floor plan with solid wood floors, picture glass windows and vaulted ceilings! In keeping with true island style, there are outdoor showers to rinse off from your day at the beach, and an outdoor barbecue area to enjoy family gatherings! Experience true island living! This is an incredible opportunity to acquire one of Maui's most amazing and irreplaceable properties! Also available for purchase is the one acre vacant parcel directly across the lane: 38 Kapohue Road MLS #365993. Property includes a 5/8" county water meter and underground electric and cable. Create an incredible Island Estate and family Compound with both Parcels!

The Jewel of Kipahulu! A picturesque gated property, nearby the treasured Seven Sacred Pools, - ideal for swimming, picnicking, fishing, hiking and glorious waterfalls – awaits you. Be instantly astonished by the magnificent pastoral land, impeccable ocean views, and soft sounds of surf rolling onto the shore. As you stroll along the landscaped property, you gaze at miles of pristine coastline, then at the crest of the hill, awaits another expansive view of the mighty blue Pacific and your breath is taken away. Build your dream home on this one of a kind clandestine estate that includes a private water source. Fully equipped ocean view cottage situated on property. Only two miles from Kipahulu National Park and the Seven Sacred Pools (Oheo Gulch). Seller financing available to qualified buyers, and seller would entertain a trade for another property in Charleston SC or Savannah GA areas. Potential for subdividing of property. Call today for a private tour.

What a fabulous house this is. Located on the lush east end of Molokai this house overlooks an ancient fishpond with Maui as the back drop. This property is very unique; when the tide is high the water is under the house and when the tide is low you have a beautiful manicured lawn. This is a 3 bedroom 3 bathroom house. If you love to cook and entertain, there is a large great room with a dining area, kitchen with an island, a very nice size living room and a small wet bar off to the side. Upstairs has a loft for an office, a lot of storage space and it over looks the living room/kitchen below. The master bedroom is huge and has it's own living room area with views to the ocean. It's has it's own bathroom that is equipped with a jacuzzi tub that looks over the fishpond and the ocean, with a separate glass block shower, his and her own sinks and a large walk in closet. The garage is a two car garage with lots of storage. Behind the garage has a small kitchenette, and a bathroom with a room for a live in caretaker, your in laws or even your teenager when they're making trouble. The house is surrounded by covered decks which is perfect for relaxing and capturing the trade winds coming across the channel. Included with the sale of this property is a 27 foot Shamrock motor boat. This property would be perfect for you; and if you don't plan on staying year round then it would make a perfect vacation rental for some extra income. This property is not a vacation property at this time and one would have to apply for a county permit. Currently it is a long term rental. Comes furnished.

Great Beach House on one of the best waterfront streets in Maui. Walk to parks, restaurants, shops, schools and the best Kihei has to offer. Older home and cottage have recently been remodeled into a charming Hawaiiana style Beach Retreat. Great lot with a seawall would be perfect for a brand new luxury home to match the many new ones on the street but the house can be used as-is until the plans and construction process is done. There is room for a swimming pool that faces the Ocean. Cottage has also been recently re-done and would be perfect for a caretaker or family member as well as a great income producer. Great storage for beach toys. Any offer or acceptance on the property shall be subject to an "As Is Addendum" agreed to by Buyer and Seller. Easy to show.

Hale Honokeana Cove presents itself as the quintessential Hawaiian oceanfront estate in the boutique gated community of Papaua Place. 3 Bedrooms and 4 Bathrooms with a well thought out floor plan of approximately 3700 square feet allows ample space for families to enjoy the sense of place this property exudes. A rustic rock staircase allows for easy access to the world renowned Honokeana Cove, famous for its phenomenal snorkeling teeming with sea turtles as well as great surf during the winter months. This home underwent a recent extensive renovation in 2014 allowing for impeccable modern finishes and current technology throughout. This home has some of the most amazing white water ocean and bay views that Maui has to offer! Contact a local Realtor to schedule a private showing.

Eureka! Maui's Premier North Shore location, no other piece of real estate on Maui's north shore compares to this cliff top luxury home. This gated home of 3 bedroom 3 bath, that is self sustaining with Solar and Private Water, blends beautifully above Maliko Gulch. The private 1.35 acre provides endless shoreline views of breaking waves, and ocean activity rarely viewed or experienced any where else on Maui. Enjoy the luxurious private heated pool, photovoltaic, private well, only minutes to Mama's Fish House, Paia and the airport.

Your very own Garden of Eden awaits at this phenomenal North Shore OCEANFRONT Estate. Five permitted structures on two acres of land including 200 feet of ocean frontage in a very peaceful, private setting. The incredible ocean and cliff views and radiant surrounds are sensory delights! Imagine watching whales and dolphins play in Waipio Bay without leaving your own back yard. Even better - experience the thrill from one of three cliff side hot tubs! The landscaping is mature and lush with a wide variety of tall exotic palms, fruit trees (limes, lemons, oranges, grapefruit, papayas, bananas, lychee, starfruit, macadamia nuts, mangoes and more), bountiful organic veggie gardens and a beautiful screen house. Relax and rejuvenate in the breathtaking surrounds or refresh in your in-ground pool with waterfall. This dream property with a 4 bedroom main house, a 2 bedroom guest house, and a studio cottage - all built to focus on the dynamic ocean views ~ could be ideal as a family compound or retreat. There's also a spacious studio above the 4 car garage and an additional studio garden cottage. Ideally located ~ approximately 20 minutes drive from Paia or 30 minutes from the airport. Compare the Oceanfront Huelo Point Estate to other oceanfront properties and experience this exceptional property and value for yourself.

Currently the only oceanfront estate available in the highly desired Spreckelsville community on the North Shore of Maui. Unparalleled views of the North Shore, West Maui Mountains and Molokai with oceanfront access to some of the world's most coveted windsurfing grounds make this estate irreplaceable. The elegant Plantation style architecture lend to the seamless flow of the home . Originally built in 1933, the home was meticulously restored in 1995 keeping with the original plantation theme but adding modern touches to include central air conditioning. Reminiscent of Old Hawai'i, the original fir hardwood floors run throughout the home giving it an authentic Island feel. The four bedrooms and three full bathrooms are thoughtfully placed for privacy and access to views of the ocean and mountains. A large pool and spa separate the main residence and the guest cottage, offering privacy and ample room for multiple guests. The gated grass lawn area and expansive oceanfront lanai lend to casual outdoor living and entertaining. The home is being offered fully furnished, excluding personal artwork and belongings. A water enthusiast's dream and a once in a lifetime opportunity to own a true Maui legacy property.

The charm and grace of old Hawaii are captured in the architecture and landscaping of this thoughtfully restored oceanfront estate. The property includes the main building which is connected to two cottages by covered walkways, plus a free standing garage/workshop. Dramatic ocean views, both coastal and across `Alenuihaha Channel to the Big Island, combined with mature tropical landscaping, create a serene retreat. Minutes from the world famous Hamoa Beach and within walking distance of Waioka Pond (Venus Pool).

OCEAN FRONT LAHAINA TOWN! Rare opportunity to build your DREAM HOME or remodel existing older home. Walk to town, swim, snorkel, stand up paddle, kayak right in your back yard! Best buy on ocean front property!

Oceanfront home on the Gold Coast for under $1,600,000!!! Home needs some love (maybe true love), but it is there and being lived in. The property is incredible: surf - fish - dive - sail - paddle right off your property. Easy access to the ocean and wonderful white sand beach two lots to the north for picnics and volleyball! Live the dream - live on the ocean!
